DATA.guide:
Available Facilities:Tourist information center, tourist hotel, interpretation center, souvenir shop, duty-free shop, nightlife restaurant exclusively for foreigners, etc.
Restrooms:Restrooms at the department store, hotel, Lotte World Amusement Park and 12 public restrooms in the neighboring areas are available.
Facilities for the Handicapped:Elevators are available at Lotte Department Store and Lotte Hotel; 
Parking spaces exclusively for the disabled are available in the shopping malls; 
Crosswalk signals are available;
Taxi service exclusively for the disabled to access downtown or the airport is available.
Interpretation Services Offered:Staff at the department store and amusement park speak some-what fluent English.
